                            <comment id="12421921" author="klaasm" created="Tue, 18 Jul 2006 20:02:32 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;TestCase demonstrating the issue and patch to WordDelimiterFilter which corrects it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Resolution: if catenate and generate are off, the filter skips to the next token instead of throwing an exception.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12421957" author="yseeley@gmail.com" created="Tue, 18 Jul 2006 21:37:02 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed.  Thanks Mike!&lt;br/&gt;
